<section class="section cpf-s5">
  <div class="container--narrow">

    <h2 class="cpf-s5__heading">
      What To Expect During Your Chemical Peel Experience
    </h2>

    <p class="cpf-s5__intro">
      Every step is designed for your safety and optimal results. Here's exactly what happens during your treatment at our Millburn spa.
    </p>

    <ol class="cpf-s5__steps">

      <li class="cpf-s5__step">
        <div class="cpf-s5__step-number" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
        <div class="cpf-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="cpf-s5__step-title">Consultation &amp; Skin Assessment (5-10 minutes)</h3>
          <p class="cpf-s5__step-text">Your treatment begins with a comprehensive skin analysis to determine the best peel type and strength for your concerns. Our expert esthetician reviews your skin history, current products, and goals to create a customized treatment plan that delivers results safely.</p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="cpf-s5__step">
        <div class="cpf-s5__step-number" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
        <div class="cpf-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="cpf-s5__step-title">Deep Cleansing &amp; Preparation (10-15 minutes)</h3>
          <p class="cpf-s5__step-text">Your skin is thoroughly cleansed and degreased to remove all oils, makeup, and impurities. We apply a prep solution that ensures even peel penetration and optimal results. Your eyes and lips are carefully protected throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="cpf-s5__step">
        <div class="cpf-s5__step-number" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
        <div class="cpf-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="cpf-s5__step-title">Chemical Peel Application (15-25 minutes)</h3>
          <p class="cpf-s5__step-text">The peel solution is applied in thin, even layers using precise techniques. You'll feel a mild tingling or warming sensation as the peel works. We monitor your skin's response carefully and neutralize the peel at the perfect time for your skin type and tolerance level.</p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="cpf-s5__step">
        <div class="cpf-s5__step-number" aria-hidden="true">4</div>
        <div class="cpf-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="cpf-s5__step-title">Neutralization &amp; Aftercare (10-15 minutes)</h3>
          <p class="cpf-s5__step-text">The peel is neutralized and removed completely, followed by application of soothing serums and protective moisturizers. You'll receive detailed aftercare instructions and products to ensure proper healing and maximize your results.</p>
        </div>
      </li>

    </ol>

    <div class="cpf-s5__comfort-note">
      <h3 class="cpf-s5__comfort-heading">Completely Comfortable &amp; Safe</h3>
      <p class="cpf-s5__comfort-text">Most clients experience only mild tingling during the peel application. Any discomfort is temporary and manageable. We monitor your skin closely and can adjust the treatment if needed to ensure your complete comfort and safety.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

